-- Finmeccanica Reiterates the Defense Company Has Never Created Slush Funds
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2010-11-22T15:49:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-22/finmeccanica-reiterates-the-defense-company-has-never-created-slush-funds.html
Finmeccanica SpA reiterated it has
never created slush funds either in Italy or abroad and it’s
willing to provide any information that could be useful to
authorities, according to a statement distributed by the Italian
exchange.  Italy’s biggest defense company said news reports about a
corruption probe is hurting the company’s shares.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  